SALES MANAGER (FOR OIL & GAS)
Baron Emperor International
Location:
Shaikh Zayed Road, Dubai
Date: 06-05-2014
Payrate: Starting at 10,000 Monthly (AED)
Salary Details:
VISA + CAR + COMMISSION + SIM CARD
Job Type: Employee
Job Status: Full Time
Categories:
Engineering & Construction
Oil & Gas
Managerial
Sales & Business Development
Baron Emperor International
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
1. Play a pivotal role in achieving the sales targets and eventually generates revenue for the organization.
2. Responsible for meeting the sales targets of the organization through effective planning and budgeting.
3. Motivate the Senior Sales Engineer in meeting the target or monthly sales quota to maintain a good sales inflow.
4. Devises strategies and techniques necessary for achieving the sales targets
5. Map potential customers and generate leads for the organization by looking forward to generating new opportunities for the organization.
6. Visit potential customers to sell the products and gain new markets/customers without time constraints or sell even under pressure, to contact clients by phone or meeting to negotiate/to follow-up terms of an agreement and conclude sales.
7. Maintaining relationships/database with existing customers through regular review visits and gaining a clear under standing of customers' businesses and requirements from bid tenders, on-going project sales and after-sales service.
8. Maximizes his sales potential and of company's product to meet his minimum monthly quota and be a team member to achieve the sales department's annual target while ensuring the commercial success of company's with their high-profile brands and products.
9. Advising on forthcoming project developments and discussing the same to weekly sales meeting in order to contribute team sales improvements.
10. Keep up a sound market knowledge and vast customer contacts in the Construction : MEP & Oil and Gas sector in UAE / GCC.
11. Initiates professional, dynamic & constant sales & business development attributes with awareness in sales operations, in terms of order deliveries and execution oversight.
12. Superb business etiquette displayed when dealing with international suppliers and local or overseas customers and their total satisfaction.
Requirements
Experience of 10 years, with proven record of impressive achievements in selling/trading/exclusive representations of below similar line of products:
a. Pipes & Fittings (OCTG, CS seamless pipes, flanges, gaskets, etc.)
b. Mechanical Products (rotating equipment)
c. Valves (various types)
d. Control & Instrumentation (gauges, monitors, leak detection, etc.)
e. Drilling Equipment & Spares
Has a wide knowledge of the Industry & Market in Construction & Petroleum in UAE or GCC
Has managed or handled employees/Sales Engineers
Must be Male, 30-40 years
Indian Nationality
Hold a Diploma in Mechanical Engineering
